T1  - Heterogeneous shareholders and signaling with share repurchases
AU  - Persons, John C.
JO  - Journal of Corporate Finance
VL  - 3
IS  - 3
SP  - 221
EP  - 249
PY  - 1997
DA  - 1997/06/01/
SN  - 0929-1199
